name: China Republican period female student uniform
description:
China Republican period female student uniform

It is a school uniform for girls of China Republican period,especially in May Fourth Movement period, so I called it 54female.

It is usually as blue upper & black lower, and u can also generate another color with this style.
I am struggling to mix the lora and some prompt such as "Ripped clothes","torn","broken", but failed, so, If some guys do it well, please let me know.
